cu.explanation_en: Setting the S1U port to an out-of-range value of 99999 will cause the gNB to fail during initialization as the port number exceeds the valid range (0-65535).

du.explanation_en: Setting the physical cell ID to a negative value of -1 will cause the gNB to fail during initialization as the value must be non-negative.
du.explanation_zh: 將物理小區 ID 設定為負值 -1 會導致 gNB 在初始化期間失敗，因為該值必須為非負數。
